CI: Switch to pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish@release/v1

  Warning:  You are using "pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish@master". The

  supported version. If you want to pin to v1 major version, use
  "pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish@release/v1". If you feel adventurous, you
  may opt to use use "pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish@unstable/v1" instead.
  A more general recommendation is to pin to exact tags or commit shas.
